metadata.description:
Show your love and support for Ethereum by purchasing this limited-time rare Ethereum on the Water collectible NFT.

Included with the token is the actual image with "preview image" text removed. The token files includes a small image and large image.

This is the first token in the collectible art EthOnTheWater series, no more than 50 will be made for this series!
